data.title: Res. List: Page 1 of 172
data.meta_description: ФОП - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a consolidated list of individuals and entities sanctioned by the United Nations Security Council. It includes 19 entries for individuals with basic identifying information like name, date of birth, nationality, and details of sanctions. The document also provides links to websites with additional information on de-listing requests and INTERPOL notices for listed individuals.
